Survey Shows 58 Percent of Germans Mistrust the Euro, Bild Says

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-05-15T10:22:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/survey-shows-58-percent-of-germans-mistrust-the-euro-bild-says.html
The percentage of Germans whose trust
in the single European currency is “very low” or “quite low”
has increased by 4 percent since December to 58 percent,  Bild am
Sonntag  newspaper reported.  According to the survey, carried out by Emnid, 48 percent
of respondents said further financial aid for  Greece  was right,
with 41 percent rejecting such a move, Bild said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
 jblack25@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  